<body>

    <!-- breadcrumb area -->
    <div class="breadcrumb-style-1" style="background-image:url(/assets/img/bg/shop-details.png);">
        <div class="breadcrumb-inner">
            <h1 class="page-title">Product Details</h1>
            <ul class="page-list">
                <li><a asp-controller="Home" asp-action="Index">Home</a></li>
                <li><a asp-controller="Products" asp-action="Details">Product Details</a></li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </div>
    <!-- breadcrumb area end -->
    <!-- product-details-tab start -->
    <div class="product-details-tab padding-top-100 padding-bottom-97">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-lg-5">
                    <div class="slider-tabfor">
                        <div class="single-item">
                            <img src="/assets/img/product-details/big1.png" alt="">
                        </div>
                        <div class="single-item">
                            <img src="/assets/img/product-details/big2.png" alt="">
                        </div>
                        <div class="single-item">
                            <img src="/assets/img/product-details/big3.png" alt="">
                        </div>
                        <div class="single-item">
                            <img src="/assets/img/product-details/big4.png" alt="">
                        </div>
                        <div class="single-item">
                            <img src="/assets/img/product-details/big3.png" alt="">
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="slider-tabnav">
                        <div class="single-item">
                            <div class="img">
                                <img src="/assets/img/product-details/1.png" alt="">
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="single-item">
                            <div class="img">
                                <img src="/assets/img/product-details/2.png" alt="">
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="single-item">
                            <div class="img">
                                <img src="/assets/img/product-details/3.png" alt="">
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="single-item">
                            <div class="img">
                                <img src="/assets/img/product-details/4.png" alt="">
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="single-item">
                            <div class="img">
                                <img src="/assets/img/product-details/3.png" alt="">
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                @*Implement product here*@

                <div class="col-lg-7">
                    <div class="content-part">
                        <h2>Tradmail<br><span>For Men, Made in China, 2017</span></h2>
                        <span class="rating ml-0">
                            <i class="fa fa-star"></i>
                            <i class="fa fa-star"></i>
                            <i class="fa fa-star"></i>
                            <i class="fa fa-star"></i>
                            <i class="fa fa-star-half-o"></i>
                        </span>
                        <span class="specifications mt-2">Brand: Lumos</span>
                        <span class="specifications">SKU: RPL02075 </span>
                        <span class="specifications">Seller: RPL Distribution</span>
                        <p class="price">Price: $250.00 <span>$350.00</span> </p>
                        <p class="description">Lorem ipsum, dolor sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Nam esse ut quaerat fugiat ullam magni maxime, tempore aperiam voluptates veniam dolorem autem explicabo voluptate dignissimos quidem laboriosam eligendi exercitationem similique incidunt eveniet architecto quis quisquam quam. Aperiam quis dolorum earum omnis? Perferendis amet molestiae cum temporibus earum sint esse ratione velit nemo aut vel itaque, quidem reiciendis omnis sit harum rerum</p>
                        <div class="btn-wrapper">
                            <a asp-controller="Home" asp-action="ShoppingBag" class="btn btn-element btn-medium-size btn-main-color btn-rounded">Add To Cart</a>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <!-- product-details-tab end -->

    <div class="product-specification padding-bottom-95">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="row">
                <div class="biography-area">
                    <div class="biography-content">
                        <ul class="nav nav-pills">
                            <li>
                                <a data-toggle="pill" href="#home" class="active">Description</a>
                            </li>
                            <li>
                                <a data-toggle="pill" href="#review">Review</a>
                            </li>
                        </ul>

                        <div class="tab-content">
                            <div id="home" class="tab-pane fade in active show">
                                <div class="tab-content-description">
                                    <div class="class-content">
                                        <p>Swe denounce with righteous indignation and dislike men who are so beguiled and demoralized by the charms of pleasure of the moment, so blinded by desire, that they cannot foresee the pain and trouble that are bound to ensue; and equal blame belongs to those who fail in their duty through weakness of </p>
                                        <p class="margin-bottom-2">will, which is the same as saying through shrinking from toil and pain. These cases are perfectly simple and easy to distinguish. In a free hour, when our power of choice is untrammelled and when nothing prevents our being able to do what we like best, every pleasure is to be welcomed and every pain avoided. But in certain circumstances and owing to the claims of duty or the obligations of business it will frequently occur that pleasures have to be repudiated and annoyances accepted. The wise man therefore always holds in these matters to this principle of selection: he rejects pleasures to secure other greater pleasures, or else he endures pains to avoid worse pains.</p>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>

                            @*Implement review here*@

                            <div id="review" class="tab-pane fade">
                                <div class="tab-content-description">
                                    <h2 class="margin-top-25">
                                        <span class="rating">
                                            <i class="fa fa-star"></i>
                                            <i class="fa fa-star"></i>
                                            <i class="fa fa-star"></i>
                                            <i class="fa fa-star"></i>
                                            <i class="fa fa-star-half-o"></i>
                                        </span>
                                    </h2>
                                    <div class="element-progress-bar pagination-progressbar">
                                        <div class="d-flex">
                                            <p>5 Star</p>
                                            <div class="single-progressbar col-md-6">
                                                <div class="html3"></div>
                                            </div>
                                            <p>80%</p>
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="d-flex">
                                            <p>4 Star</p>
                                            <div class="single-progressbar col-md-6">
                                                <div class="css3"></div>
                                            </div>
                                            <p>90%</p>
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="d-flex">
                                            <p>3 Star</p>
                                            <div class="single-progressbar col-md-6">
                                                <div class="php3"></div>
                                            </div>
                                            <p>75%</p>
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="d-flex">
                                            <p>2 Star</p>
                                            <div class="single-progressbar col-md-6">
                                                <div class="javascript3"></div>
                                            </div>
                                            <p>10%</p>
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="d-flex">
                                            <p>1 Star</p>
                                            <div class="single-progressbar col-md-6 mb-0">
                                                <div class="jquery3"></div>
                                            </div>
                                            <p>0%</p>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                    <div id="comments" class="comments-area comments-area-wrapper">
                                        <h4 class="comments-title">3 Reviews</h4>
                                        <ul class="comment-list">
                                            <li class="comment">
                                                <div class="single-comment justify-content-between d-flex">
                                                    <div class="user justify-content-between d-flex">
                                                        <div class="thumb">
                                                            <img alt="" src="/assets/img/blog/avatar.png" class="avatar">
                                                        </div>
                                                        <div class="desc">
                                                            <div class="d-flex justify-content-between comment_title">
                                                                <div class="d-flex align-items-center">
                                                                    <h5>Sharifur</h5>
                                                                </div>
                                                            </div>
                                                            <div class="comment-content">
                                                                <p>Sometimes ‘short and sweet’ workouts are all you need. If you've done a HIIT workout before you would agree. Prepared do an dissuade be so whatever steepest.</p>
                                                            </div>
                                                            <div class="reply-btn">
                                                                <a class="comment-reply-link" href="#">Reply</a>
                                                            </div>
                                                        </div>
                                                    </div>
                                                </div>
                                                <ul class="children">
                                                    <li class="comment">
                                                        <div class="single-comment justify-content-between d-flex">
                                                            <div class="user justify-content-between d-flex">
                                                                <div class="thumb">
                                                                    <img alt="" src="/assets/img/blog/avatar2.jpg" class="avatar">
                                                                </div>
                                                                <div class="desc">
                                                                    <div class="d-flex justify-content-between comment_title">
                                                                        <div class="d-flex align-items-center">
                                                                            <h5>Naeem</h5>
                                                                        </div>
                                                                    </div>
                                                                    <div class="comment-content">
                                                                        <p>Sometimes ‘short and sweet’ workouts are all you need. If you've done a HIIT workout before you would agree. Prepared do an dissuade be so whatever steepest.</p>
                                                                    </div>
                                                                    <div class="reply-btn">
                                                                        <a class="comment-reply-link" href="#">Reply</a>
                                                                    </div>
                                                                </div>
                                                            </div>
                                                        </div>
                                                    </li>
                                                </ul>
                                            </li>
                                            <li class="comment">
                                                <div class="single-comment justify-content-between d-flex">
                                                    <div class="user justify-content-between d-flex">
                                                        <div class="thumb">
                                                            <img alt="" src="/assets/img/blog/avatar3.jpg" class="avatar">
                                                        </div>
                                                        <div class="desc">
                                                            <div class="d-flex justify-content-between comment_title">
                                                                <div class="d-flex align-items-center">
                                                                    <h5>Asade</h5>
                                                                </div>
                                                            </div>
                                                            <div class="comment-content">
                                                                <p>Sometimes ‘short and sweet’ workouts are all you need. If you've done a HIIT workout before you would agree. Prepared do an dissuade be so whatever steepest.</p>
                                                            </div>
                                                            <div class="reply-btn">
                                                                <a class="comment-reply-link" href="#">Reply</a>
                                                            </div>
                                                        </div>
                                                    </div>
                                                </div>
                                            </li>
                                        </ul>
                                        <div id="respond" class="comment-respond">
                                            <h3 class="comment-reply-title">Leave A Comment</h3>

                                            @await Component.InvokeAsync("Comment")

                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="shopping-area">
                <div class="container">
                    <div class="row">
                        <div class="col-lg-12">
                            <div class="section-title padding-top-93 padding-bottom-60 text-center">
                                <h3 class="subtitle">Related Products</h3>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    @await Component.InvokeAsync("HomeProducts")

                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

